---
title: Shroom ’n’ Swiss Pork Burgers with Potato Wedges & a Creamy Honey Dijon Dipper
description: Not to get cheesy, but we’re head over heels for these bodacious burgers. Juicy pork patties are topped with an ultra-savory combo of Swiss cheese and sautéed mushrooms, then tucked into toasty buns. Served with a heap of crispy oven fries and honey Dijon sauce, it’ll be tough not to pig out.
